OL,3,CMan's loyalist 'show of strength'
OL,4,Cconviction quashed by appeal court
OL,6,FA man jailed for taking part in a so-
OL,7,Fcalled loyalist show of strength in
OL,8,Feast Belfast is set to have his
OL,9,Fconviction quashed, the Court of
OL,10,FAppeal ruled today.
OL,12,FSenior judges held Derek Lammey was
OL,13,Fwrongly found guilty of intimidation
OL,14,Fon the basis of voice recognition
OL,15,Fevidence from police officers.
OL,17,FThe 60-year-old, will now be freed
OL,18,Ffrom prison after prosecutors were
OL,19,Fdenied a retrial.
