OL,3,CMan's loyalist 'show of strength'
OL,4,Cconviction quashed by appeal court
OL,6,FLammey had been convicted in
OL,7,Fconnection with a gathering of up to
OL,8,F40 masked men at Pitt Park in February
OL,9,F2021.
OL,11,FThe group gathered in the area and
OL,12,Fwalked to a nearby community centre
OL,13,Fwhere a number of women and children
OL,14,Fwere taking shelter.
OL,16,FThose inside the building included the
OL,17,Fwife and daughter of murdered east
OL,18,FBelfast man Ian Ogle.
