OL,3,CMan's loyalist 'show of strength'
OL,4,Cconviction quashed by appeal court
OL,6,FMr Ogle was beaten and stabbed to
OL,7,Fdeath near his home at Cluan Place
OL,8,Fback in January 2019.
OL,10,FFollowing a non-jury trial at Belfast
OL,11,FCrown Court last year, Lammey was
OL,12,Facquitted on separate charges of
OL,13,Funlawful assembly and affray over the
OL,14,FPitt Park incident.
OL,16,FBut the judge found him guilty of
OL,17,Fintimidation through taking part in
OL,18,Fwhat was described as a show of
OL,19,Fstrength by an unspecified loyalist
OL,20,Forganisation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
