OL,3,CMan's loyalist 'show of strength'
OL,4,Cconviction quashed by appeal court
OL,6,FCo-accused Stephen Matthews, 62, of
OL,7,FPansy Street in Belfast, was cleared
OL,8,Fon all charges of involvement with the
OL,9,Fmasked group.
OL,11,FLammey, who received an 18-month
OL,12,Fsentence, centred his challenge to the
OL,13,Fconviction on identification evidence
OL,14,Ffrom two police officers who recorded
OL,15,Fthe incident on body-worn cameras.
OL,17,FThey both claimed to have recognised
OL,18,Fhis voice as being one of the crowd at
OL,19,Fthe scene.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
