OL,3,CMan's loyalist 'show of strength'
OL,4,Cconviction quashed by appeal court
OL,6,FDefence lawyers told the Court of
OL,7,FAppeal it was mere assertions from non-
OL,8,Fexperts without any further context
OL,9,Ffor their attributions.
OL,11,FBarrister Joseph O'Keeffe KC argued
OL,12,Fthat the officers' evidence wrongly
OL,13,Fbecame the determining factor in
OL,14,FLammey being found guilty of
OL,15,Fintimidation.
OL,17,F"In a case of someone passing by,
OL,18,Fspeaking at maximum four words behind
OL,19,Fa mask and outside, it is hard to
OL,20,Fimagine worse circumstances to
OL,21,Frecognise a voice," he submitted.
