OL,3,CMan's loyalist 'show of strength'
OL,4,Cconviction quashed by appeal court
OL,6,F"This conviction cannot be said to be
OL,7,Fsafe and must be quashed," she held.
OL,9,FFollowing the ruling, prosecution
OL,10,Fcounsel sought to have Lammey stand
OL,11,Ftrial again on the intimidation charge.
OL,13,FBut citing the passage of time and six-
OL,14,Fmonth period Lammey has spent behind
OL,15,Fbars, the Lady Chief Justice
OL,16,Fconfirmed: "We do not consider this is
OL,17,Fa case where we should order a
OL,18,Fretrial."
