OL,6,FOutside court Lammey's solicitor,
OL,7,FMagan Burns of Phoenix Law, welcomed
OL,8,Fthe verdict.
OL,10,FShe said: "This is a classic example
OL,11,Fof the dangers of police officers
OL,12,Fseeking to rely on familiarity to
OL,13,Fground identifications, as opposed to
OL,14,Findependent evidence."
